19:T432,Internal evidence clearly identifies this as ARMAR LPS Clavicle Hook Plate 3.5 manufactured by Meril Life Sciences with titanium (TiCP) construction. However, external sources (DePuy Synthes LCP) describe similar 3.5mm clavicle hook plates with identical indications. CONFLICT: Current classification shows manufacturer=Meril Life Sciences but product naming (LPS) could suggest confusion with DePuy Synthes LCP (Locking Compression Plate) system. The ARMAR branding suggests this is Meril's proprietary system, but LPS acronym meaning requires verification—likely 'Locking Plate System' in Meril context vs. DePuy's 'LCP'. Clinical function is verified: hook plates for lateral clavicle fractures and AC joint injuries with multiple depth options (12/15/18mm) for anatomical variation. Material (titanium CP), thickness (4.0mm), and indications are internally consistent. Recommendation: Send to review to confirm (1) ARMAR LPS is distinct Meril product line, (2) verify LPS acronym meaning, (3) confirm no trademark/branding issues with similar DePuy naming conventions.15:["$","$L18",null,{"product":{"product_name":"LPS Clavicle Hook Plate 3.5","product_name_display":"LPS Clavicle Hook Plate 3.5","sku_code":"MT-PT440X0XXL/R","product_family":"ARMAR LPS Clavicle Hook Plate 3.5","product_family_display":"ARMAR LPS Clavicle Hook Plate 3.5","slug":"lps-clavicle-hook-plate-3.5","images":[{"id":"prop_69c2d2d","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c2d2d07171238d2edca596/cover_637a9a77.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Pulsage Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":309736,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:58:17.906012+00:00","source":"family_propagation","width":1654,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"LPS Clavicle Hook Plate 3.5 | Meril Clavicle Plates - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"The LPS Clavicle Hook Plate 3.5 is a premium titanium (TiCP) orthopedic implant designed for superior acromioclavi